WEBVTT

1
00:01:15.241 --> 00:01:16.902
INSPECTOR CHAN

2
00:01:50.076 --> 00:01:53.068
SUPER CRIME FIGHTERS

3
00:02:04.124 --> 00:02:06.251
Anyone else?

4
00:02:13.967 --> 00:02:16.595
Such a beautiful woman...

5
00:02:16.769 --> 00:02:20.136
...and you arrest her...

6
00:02:20.306 --> 00:02:23.036
...just for spitting?

7
00:02:24.177 --> 00:02:26.941
Is there no justice?

8
00:02:27.647 --> 00:02:30.207
Is there no law?

9
00:02:31.117 --> 00:02:33.779
Commissioner is only your boss...

10
00:02:33.953 --> 00:02:36.547
...because he paid his dues
to the Crocodile Gang.

11
00:02:37.323 --> 00:02:39.723
And you don't fucking know me?

12
00:02:40.226 --> 00:02:43.525
Sorry. I didn't know
she was your wife.

13
00:02:45.899 --> 00:02:47.628
Ugly coward!

14
00:02:57.911 --> 00:03:01.142
What are you looking at? Never seen
such a handsome gang boss?

15
00:03:08.021 --> 00:03:10.421
Who'd be in the film business?

16
00:03:10.590 --> 00:03:13.354
It's Sunday.
and the theater's deserted.

17
00:03:14.194 --> 00:03:15.661
Where's the car?

18
00:03:27.006 --> 00:03:28.496
Let's go back inside!

19
00:03:50.063 --> 00:03:51.587
Call for help!

20
00:03:53.733 --> 00:03:56.361
No need for that. Northerner.

21
00:03:56.536 --> 00:04:01.872
While you were messing with the cop.
your men signed up with us.

22
00:04:03.443 --> 00:04:06.378
I'll kill all you Axe Gangsters!

23
00:04:40.013 --> 00:04:44.245
Stop! You forget the time
I treated you to dinner.

24
00:04:55.295 --> 00:04:56.455
Brother Sum.

25
00:05:04.170 --> 00:05:05.296
Please...

26
00:05:07.040 --> 00:05:08.701
Please spare me.

27
00:05:09.309 --> 00:05:11.106
Don't worry.

28
00:05:11.711 --> 00:05:15.511
I don't kill women. You can go!

29
00:05:16.282 --> 00:05:17.943
Thank you. Big Brother.

30
00:05:31.998 --> 00:05:34.523
Cops! Come clean up the mess!

31
00:06:52.645 --> 00:06:56.376
THE AXE GANG

32
00:06:58.551 --> 00:07:00.480
In a time of social unrest
and disorder...

33
00:07:00.653 --> 00:07:03.451
...the gangs have moved in
to consolidate their power.

34
00:07:03.623 --> 00:07:06.057
The most feared of them all
is the Axe Gang.

35
00:07:06.225 --> 00:07:10.059
Only in the poorest districts.
which hold no interest for the gangs...

36
00:07:10.229 --> 00:07:11.890
...can people live in peace.

37
00:07:14.400 --> 00:07:16.061
PIG STY ALLE Y

38
00:07:37.023 --> 00:07:38.513
One. two. three!

39
00:07:39.592 --> 00:07:41.423
- That okay. Coolie?
- No problem!

40
00:07:59.545 --> 00:08:00.944
TAILOR

41
00:08:05.284 --> 00:08:06.683
NOODLES AND CONGEE

42
00:08:27.473 --> 00:08:30.067
My check. please. Donut.

43
00:08:32.478 --> 00:08:35.970
- How much?
- It's on the house!

44
00:08:36.182 --> 00:08:37.342
Donut.

45
00:08:37.517 --> 00:08:39.849
- It's nothing.
- I like you.

46
00:08:40.019 --> 00:08:43.011
I'll ask the wife about
lowering your rent.

47
00:08:44.657 --> 00:08:46.420
Morning. Landlord!

48
00:08:48.494 --> 00:08:49.483
Landlord!

49
00:08:49.662 --> 00:08:51.323
Jill! How you've grown!

50
00:08:51.497 --> 00:08:53.692
Come let me examine you!

51
00:09:06.345 --> 00:09:08.677
Good to see you. Landlord!

52
00:09:08.848 --> 00:09:10.338
What's so good about it?

53
00:09:10.516 --> 00:09:11.676
Don't...!

54
00:09:17.523 --> 00:09:22.859
Can you make the skirt slit higher?

55
00:09:23.529 --> 00:09:25.053
Sure!

56
00:09:25.231 --> 00:09:26.698
Look. a comet!

57
00:09:30.236 --> 00:09:31.726
Jane! You naughty girl!

58
00:09:31.904 --> 00:09:35.601
Landlord! You're such a scoundrel!

59
00:09:37.743 --> 00:09:42.737
Don't go. Jane! Stay and chat!

60
00:09:43.049 --> 00:09:46.212
I'm only kidding. Jane!

61
00:10:06.672 --> 00:10:08.071
Landlady!

62
00:10:08.874 --> 00:10:10.341
Landlady!

63
00:10:13.446 --> 00:10:15.971
What happened to the water?

64
00:10:30.429 --> 00:10:31.589
Water ain't free!

65
00:10:31.764 --> 00:10:35.996
You talk a lot for someone
who won't pay his rent.

66
00:10:36.168 --> 00:10:39.865
But I'm in the middle of a shampoo.

67
00:10:40.039 --> 00:10:41.506
You think that's a problem?

68
00:10:41.674 --> 00:10:44.700
From now on. no water on Mondays.
Wednesdays and Fridays.

69
00:10:44.877 --> 00:10:47.812
Water ration Tuesdays. Thursdays
and Saturdays.

70
00:10:47.980 --> 00:10:52.849
I just love hearing you fools
complain. Assholes!

71
00:10:53.019 --> 00:10:54.213
Good morning. Landlady!

72
00:10:54.387 --> 00:10:58.619
Just pay your rent.
or I'll burn your shop down.

73
00:10:59.358 --> 00:11:02.521
What's so funny?
Rent's no laughing matter. fairy!

74
00:11:04.497 --> 00:11:08.456
Serves you right you're a coolie!

75
00:11:08.634 --> 00:11:11.831
Months overdue and not even
a "good morning. "

76
00:11:12.004 --> 00:11:13.869
You'll be a coolie for life.

77
00:11:19.845 --> 00:11:21.710
There you go. handsome!

78
00:11:25.651 --> 00:11:28.085
What took you so long
with the congee?

79
00:11:28.254 --> 00:11:31.155
I stopped to help an old lady
cross the street.

80
00:11:31.323 --> 00:11:34.087
- What are you doing here?
- Checking for Peeping Toms.

81
00:11:34.260 --> 00:11:36.490
Was someone just spying on you.
Auntie Six?

82
00:11:36.662 --> 00:11:40.223
Don't shoot your mouth off
without proof.

83
00:11:43.335 --> 00:11:46.270
She's crazy.

84
00:12:18.804 --> 00:12:20.533
Go away!

85
00:12:39.558 --> 00:12:41.958
Please can you teach us. sir?

86
00:12:42.128 --> 00:12:43.220
No more soccer!

87
00:13:19.532 --> 00:13:21.762
- Who wants the cut?
- My boss.

88
00:13:24.436 --> 00:13:25.596
Take a seat.

89
00:13:36.482 --> 00:13:38.973
Done! Fifty cents. please.

90
00:13:40.452 --> 00:13:42.010
Isn't it great?

91
00:13:42.288 --> 00:13:43.812
It's too good!

92
00:13:44.690 --> 00:13:46.851
Why'd you make him look so good?

93
00:13:47.560 --> 00:13:48.959
Why?

94
00:13:56.368 --> 00:14:00.031
Don't get mad. boss.
He's my old buddy. I'll handle this.

95
00:14:02.041 --> 00:14:05.704
He's boss of the Axe Gang. Don't you
see the two axes? We're bad guys.

96
00:14:05.878 --> 00:14:08.711
Making him look good
is really bad. Understand?

97
00:14:08.881 --> 00:14:11.179
- I didn't know.
- You're a numskull!

98
00:14:11.417 --> 00:14:14.978
But I like you. so just pay me.
and I'll take care of it.

99
00:14:15.154 --> 00:14:16.212
No way!

100
00:14:18.490 --> 00:14:22.256
Steady with the axe. boss.
Let me talk to him.

101
00:14:24.430 --> 00:14:27.991
I really care for you. You saw it
for yourself. Seriously.

102
00:14:28.167 --> 00:14:32.501
Why don't you pay up. Not much.
Enough for a drink.

103
00:14:32.671 --> 00:14:34.832
Oh. so it's blackmail!

104
00:14:36.675 --> 00:14:38.006
Boss!

105
00:14:38.844 --> 00:14:40.004
Boss!

106
00:14:43.849 --> 00:14:47.012
Now you're dead!

107
00:14:47.186 --> 00:14:49.711
Looks like he's waking up!

108
00:14:49.889 --> 00:14:51.220
I'm not afraid.

109
00:14:51.390 --> 00:14:53.358
You can kill me.

110
00:14:53.525 --> 00:14:56.926
But there'll be thousands more of me!

111
00:15:00.132 --> 00:15:03.397
You want to play tough? The Axe
Gang boss is napping in there.

112
00:15:03.569 --> 00:15:05.366
Whoever wants to die.
step forward.

113
00:15:07.706 --> 00:15:10.140
So you want to fight?

114
00:15:10.309 --> 00:15:13.369
Great! We'll go one-on-one.

115
00:15:13.545 --> 00:15:16.708
Don't even think about cheating.

116
00:15:17.082 --> 00:15:18.709
That old woman with the onion!

117
00:15:21.053 --> 00:15:26.389
You look real tough. Want to try me?
I'll let you hit me first.

118
00:15:31.096 --> 00:15:32.495
What do you do?

119
00:15:32.665 --> 00:15:34.394
I'm a farmer.

120
00:15:34.566 --> 00:15:38.058
Farmers don't fight. Piss off!

121
00:15:38.237 --> 00:15:39.602
He's crazy!

122
00:15:39.772 --> 00:15:41.296
Calling me names?

123
00:15:41.473 --> 00:15:44.067
You're lucky you're a woman.

124
00:15:45.277 --> 00:15:50.510
Hey. shorty! Yeah. you!
If you're short. you don't retort.

125
00:15:53.519 --> 00:15:57.421
What did I say about cheating?

126
00:15:57.589 --> 00:15:58.851
Sit back down!

127
00:16:01.860 --> 00:16:04.522
You! The geezer with the glasses.
You look mean.

128
00:16:07.700 --> 00:16:10.828
No. not you. I mean...

129
00:16:11.003 --> 00:16:12.129
You!

130
00:16:12.304 --> 00:16:15.034
Hey. kid. let's rumble!

131
00:16:16.976 --> 00:16:18.807
All right. all right!

132
00:16:19.111 --> 00:16:22.672
So no one-on-ones today.

133
00:16:22.848 --> 00:16:25.043
You're all such wimps!

134
00:16:27.953 --> 00:16:30.114
He blackmailed me.

135
00:16:30.522 --> 00:16:33.685
Fat woman. you're
in charge here. right?

136
00:16:33.859 --> 00:16:35.622
Fat woman. my ass!

137
00:16:35.861 --> 00:16:37.556
I'm with the Axe Gang!

138
00:16:37.730 --> 00:16:38.856
Axe Gang. my ass!

139
00:16:39.031 --> 00:16:40.020
Boss!

140
00:16:40.199 --> 00:16:41.791
Boss. my ass!

141
00:16:42.034 --> 00:16:44.229
- You have to pay our medical bills!
- Bills. my ass!

142
00:16:44.403 --> 00:16:46.667
- We're on the same side!
- Same side. my ass!

143
00:16:50.342 --> 00:16:52.970
Think you're so tough?
I'll call for backup!

144
00:16:53.212 --> 00:16:57.649
You nitwit! Let's see you call backup!

145
00:16:58.984 --> 00:17:02.647
You don't know the backup I have.
I'm talking an army here.

146
00:17:04.156 --> 00:17:08.820
Don't you go away! Go put
a down payment on your coffin!

147
00:17:22.408 --> 00:17:23.773
Who threw the firecracker?

148
00:17:30.015 --> 00:17:31.505
I'm one of you. brother.

149
00:17:53.872 --> 00:17:55.362
Mind your own business!

150
00:17:55.541 --> 00:17:59.033
It's raining. Go bring in your laundry!

151
00:17:59.311 --> 00:18:00.608
Fat woman!

152
00:18:13.592 --> 00:18:17.892
You blackmailing me too? I ain't afraid.

153
00:18:34.213 --> 00:18:35.202
I...

154
00:18:54.867 --> 00:18:57.893
Did anyone see what happened?

155
00:18:58.904 --> 00:19:01.566
Don't! My back's broken!

156
00:19:02.307 --> 00:19:05.037
Call for help!

157
00:19:58.263 --> 00:20:01.721
Hold on. calm down. You hungry?

158
00:20:27.025 --> 00:20:28.287
Keep quiet.

159
00:20:43.709 --> 00:20:45.108
No.

160
00:21:08.900 --> 00:21:10.458
Who did this?

161
00:21:14.339 --> 00:21:16.239
I'll count to three.

162
00:21:19.077 --> 00:21:20.237
One...

163
00:21:23.849 --> 00:21:25.817
...two...

164
00:21:37.296 --> 00:21:38.456
I did it!

165
00:24:56.261 --> 00:24:58.161
Are the goods okay. Brother Sum?

166
00:25:00.232 --> 00:25:01.460
Sorry!

167
00:25:04.603 --> 00:25:06.594
Look away. kid.

168
00:25:10.876 --> 00:25:12.207
Get rid of him!

169
00:25:13.578 --> 00:25:15.569
We're the bad guys!

170
00:25:15.747 --> 00:25:17.772
We're meant to do the ass-kicking...

171
00:25:18.750 --> 00:25:20.877
...not the other way around.

172
00:25:21.052 --> 00:25:24.385
And it's all because these morons
posed as Axes.

173
00:25:24.556 --> 00:25:27.787
Don't waste your time. Brother Sum.

174
00:25:27.959 --> 00:25:30.723
We'll handle this.

175
00:25:30.896 --> 00:25:32.796
You! Take care of it.

176
00:25:47.012 --> 00:25:52.075
- Boy. can this guy pick locks.
- It's a living. Give me a break.

177
00:25:52.250 --> 00:25:54.912
Pick that one too. if you're so good.

178
00:25:55.320 --> 00:25:56.309
Come.

179
00:25:57.022 --> 00:25:59.820
I'll count to three.

180
00:26:00.625 --> 00:26:01.649
Hurry!

181
00:26:03.395 --> 00:26:05.226
Ready? Three!

182
00:26:15.240 --> 00:26:17.037
That's quick!

183
00:26:18.376 --> 00:26:20.901
Brother Sum. we really
want to be Axes.

184
00:26:21.079 --> 00:26:23.980
That's why we did what we did.
Give us a chance.

185
00:26:24.316 --> 00:26:25.647
Ever killed anyone?

186
00:26:25.817 --> 00:26:28.308
I've always thought about it.

187
00:26:28.653 --> 00:26:30.086
Then go kill someone.

188
00:26:30.255 --> 00:26:32.223
I will!

189
00:26:33.592 --> 00:26:34.650
Go on!

190
00:26:35.060 --> 00:26:36.550
Thank you. Brother Sum.

191
00:26:48.106 --> 00:26:51.598
We can always find a use for that type.

192
00:26:55.013 --> 00:26:57.846
I told you before.
you've got to look tough.

193
00:26:58.016 --> 00:26:59.506
Tougher!

194
00:27:00.852 --> 00:27:02.615
Tougher!

195
00:27:04.689 --> 00:27:06.247
Act the part.

196
00:27:06.424 --> 00:27:07.891
And try to stay awake.

197
00:27:08.059 --> 00:27:09.424
It's tiring being tough.

198
00:27:09.594 --> 00:27:12.688
Tiring? It's our living!

199
00:27:13.832 --> 00:27:17.529
The streets out there are filled
with money and women.

200
00:27:17.702 --> 00:27:20.432
You only need the will
and determination...

201
00:27:20.605 --> 00:27:23.938
...to seize the opportunity to win.

202
00:27:24.209 --> 00:27:25.767
This is our big chance!

203
00:27:25.944 --> 00:27:28.640
We just kill someone.
and we're in the gang.

204
00:27:29.114 --> 00:27:32.606
Then it'll be money and women
all the way!

205
00:27:33.551 --> 00:27:36.418
Don't be like those beggars...

206
00:27:36.621 --> 00:27:39.351
...with no ambition.

207
00:27:44.295 --> 00:27:47.458
Who are you looking at. four-eyes?
I'll smash your glasses!

208
00:27:48.833 --> 00:27:50.460
Get lost!

209
00:27:50.802 --> 00:27:52.133
Come here and say that!

210
00:27:52.303 --> 00:27:54.464
- You're really gonna kill someone?
- That's right!

211
00:27:54.639 --> 00:27:58.234
The four-eyes. the fat woman
and all the residents of Pig Sty.

212
00:27:58.410 --> 00:28:00.173
But they're good at kung fu.

213
00:28:00.345 --> 00:28:03.178
- I can do kung fu!
- Oh. yeah?

214
00:28:05.316 --> 00:28:08.979
Didn't I tell you I know
Buddhist Palm kung fu?

215
00:28:10.789 --> 00:28:14.225
Hey there. handsome boy. Stop.

216
00:28:15.927 --> 00:28:18.657
Amazing!

217
00:28:19.064 --> 00:28:23.330
Do you know you have
a special aura?

218
00:28:23.935 --> 00:28:27.371
You're so young. but you have
the bone structure...

219
00:28:27.539 --> 00:28:30.940
and chi flow of a kung-fu genius.

220
00:28:31.509 --> 00:28:35.707
If your chi flow can be channeled.
then you will be invincible!

221
00:28:35.880 --> 00:28:39.441
Like the old saying:
You cannot escape your destiny.

222
00:28:39.918 --> 00:28:44.685
The duty of upholding worid peace
and punishing evil will be yours.

223
00:28:45.190 --> 00:28:46.179
Sure.

224
00:28:47.092 --> 00:28:50.528
This is the scroll of the Buddhist Palm.
It's priceless.

225
00:28:50.695 --> 00:28:54.222
But as it's fate.
I'll let you have it for $ 10.

226
00:28:56.568 --> 00:28:58.559
BUDDHIST PALM MANUAL

227
00:29:02.507 --> 00:29:05.067
- You gave him your life savings?
- Yes.

228
00:29:05.243 --> 00:29:08.508
I was saving to study to be
a doctor or lawyer...

229
00:29:08.680 --> 00:29:11.080
...but this was worid peace.

230
00:29:35.106 --> 00:29:37.438
Let go of the girl!

231
00:29:56.394 --> 00:29:59.227
Hey! It's the Buddhist Palm!

232
00:29:59.564 --> 00:30:01.725
"The 20-Cent Kung Fu Manual. "

233
00:30:01.900 --> 00:30:03.629
You must be loaded.

234
00:30:04.035 --> 00:30:06.196
Have you killed anyone lately?

235
00:30:17.482 --> 00:30:22.385
He's a fool. and she's mute. Losers!

236
00:30:24.155 --> 00:30:27.989
I realized then that good guys
never win. I want to be bad.

237
00:30:28.827 --> 00:30:30.920
I want to be the killer!

238
00:30:32.230 --> 00:30:34.425
- Ice cream!
- Where?

239
00:30:35.233 --> 00:30:36.996
Make mine a vanilla.

240
00:30:37.168 --> 00:30:38.533
Chocolate for me!

241
00:30:50.081 --> 00:30:53.073
What're you looking at?
Never seen free ice cream before?

242
00:30:58.523 --> 00:30:59.683
Look at her run!

243
00:31:15.039 --> 00:31:20.375
You're such kung-fu masters.
go take it on the road.

244
00:31:20.545 --> 00:31:22.877
You belong in the circus. not here!

245
00:31:23.047 --> 00:31:27.279
Don't say that. Landlady.
There must be a reason they're here.

246
00:31:27.585 --> 00:31:29.951
Everyone has his reasons.

247
00:31:30.121 --> 00:31:32.214
We don't want to make trouble.

248
00:31:32.390 --> 00:31:35.086
I'm glad you get it.
The mob's mad at us.

249
00:31:35.260 --> 00:31:38.388
We'll never hear the end of it.
Why don't you get lost!

250
00:31:39.464 --> 00:31:41.728
Your wife shouldn't be so nasty.

251
00:31:44.002 --> 00:31:45.833
You okay?

252
00:31:47.772 --> 00:31:49.296
Masters.

253
00:31:56.915 --> 00:31:58.906
We have nothing precious
to give you...

254
00:31:59.083 --> 00:32:01.415
...but take this as a token
of our appreciation.

255
00:32:02.287 --> 00:32:04.187
Thanks for saving us!

256
00:32:11.930 --> 00:32:14.922
Stop the crying. This isn't a show!

257
00:32:15.099 --> 00:32:18.660
- You're so cold-hearted.
- Talking back to me. eh?

258
00:32:18.836 --> 00:32:21.634
You may know kung fu.
but you're still a fairy.

259
00:32:24.142 --> 00:32:27.043
It's no crime to be good at kung fu!

260
00:32:27.211 --> 00:32:29.975
Once a fairy. always a fairy.

261
00:32:30.148 --> 00:32:33.675
Look at you. What's with
the red underwear?

262
00:32:33.851 --> 00:32:36.342
Why not a diaper while you're at it.

263
00:32:37.622 --> 00:32:39.647
What's wrong with red underwear?

264
00:32:39.891 --> 00:32:42.724
Where were you
when there was trouble?

265
00:32:42.894 --> 00:32:46.853
If it weren't for them. we'd be finished.
Be reasonable!

266
00:32:47.031 --> 00:32:48.521
I'll reason with you.

267
00:32:48.700 --> 00:32:51.965
You owe me three months' rent.
That's $90.

268
00:32:52.136 --> 00:32:54.400
Pay up or pack up!

269
00:32:54.572 --> 00:32:56.733
Don't you worry. I'll pay it.

270
00:32:56.908 --> 00:32:59.399
Think you're a smartass.
Rabbit-Tooth Jane?

271
00:32:59.577 --> 00:33:02.205
What's it to you. tub of lard?

272
00:33:02.380 --> 00:33:03.540
Bitch!

273
00:33:04.682 --> 00:33:06.343
Calm down. Landlady.

274
00:33:07.752 --> 00:33:09.811
This is your fault.

275
00:33:12.023 --> 00:33:14.321
- Are you trying to kill us?
- You're right.

276
00:33:14.492 --> 00:33:16.653
How could you do that?

277
00:33:16.828 --> 00:33:18.762
Shut the hell up!

278
00:33:32.010 --> 00:33:34.240
You think you can out-yell me?

279
00:33:38.349 --> 00:33:41.113
The fat lady can really sing.

280
00:33:42.153 --> 00:33:43.643
Watch this!

281
00:33:58.603 --> 00:33:59.797
What happened?

282
00:34:00.171 --> 00:34:03.106
What do you mean.
what happened? You try it.

283
00:34:03.274 --> 00:34:05.242
- Me?
- Quick!

284
00:34:11.082 --> 00:34:13.346
Sorry! You okay?

285
00:34:14.118 --> 00:34:17.451
I think you should get closer
and take better aim. Okay?

286
00:34:17.622 --> 00:34:18.611
Okay!

287
00:34:30.835 --> 00:34:33.497
- Who's throwing the handles?
- Handle?

288
00:34:35.640 --> 00:34:37.608
Where's the third knife?

289
00:34:38.276 --> 00:34:40.710
God knows where it went.

290
00:34:40.878 --> 00:34:43.346
Could it be the same one? Can't be...

291
00:34:43.514 --> 00:34:45.277
- Don't!
- Sorry.

292
00:34:47.452 --> 00:34:49.283
What are you trying to say?

293
00:34:49.454 --> 00:34:53.618
I just remembered I have
something to do. See you!

294
00:34:56.227 --> 00:34:58.286
Uh-oh. They've seen us!

295
00:34:59.797 --> 00:35:01.230
Stay back!

296
00:35:09.807 --> 00:35:13.903
Don't panic! Snakes like music.
If I whistle. they won't bite.

297
00:35:14.078 --> 00:35:15.636
Please. no more bright ideas.

298
00:35:19.750 --> 00:35:21.217
Oh. what the hell!

299
00:35:27.992 --> 00:35:29.550
Not you again. asshole!

300
00:35:29.727 --> 00:35:33.094
Get back to your business!

301
00:35:34.932 --> 00:35:36.422
Split up!

302
00:35:38.703 --> 00:35:39.863
Split?

303
00:37:52.803 --> 00:37:54.134
What're you doing here?

304
00:37:54.305 --> 00:37:56.466
Looking for you. Weren't you hurt?

305
00:37:56.641 --> 00:37:57.835
I'm fine!

306
00:37:59.910 --> 00:38:02.811
How come you always recover so fast?

307
00:38:03.147 --> 00:38:04.637
I don't know.

308
00:38:05.016 --> 00:38:07.644
- Which hospital did you go to?
- Don't remember.

309
00:38:08.419 --> 00:38:10.046
Maybe it's better that way.

310
00:38:10.221 --> 00:38:14.920
Memories can be painful.
To forget may be a blessing!

311
00:38:15.092 --> 00:38:17.925
I never knew you were so deep.

312
00:38:19.163 --> 00:38:21.654
All the sadness one can bear...

313
00:38:29.640 --> 00:38:32.905
...down the river everywhere.

314
00:38:35.212 --> 00:38:36.804
Hey. get out of the way!

315
00:38:36.981 --> 00:38:38.243
Move!

316
00:38:38.416 --> 00:38:40.077
I'll slap you to kingdom come!

317
00:38:40.451 --> 00:38:44.285
Look at those four-eyes
carting around a coffin.

318
00:38:46.123 --> 00:38:47.613
What morons!

319
00:38:49.827 --> 00:38:51.988
Don't blame me for making you leave.

320
00:38:52.163 --> 00:38:56.224
We'll let Buddha decide...

321
00:38:56.701 --> 00:38:59.101
...whether you stay...

322
00:38:59.270 --> 00:39:01.704
...or go.

323
00:39:05.609 --> 00:39:07.600
HORRIFICALLY BAD FATE

324
00:39:19.590 --> 00:39:21.353
Have some tea.

325
00:39:28.632 --> 00:39:31.692
We're grateful for
some professional help.

326
00:39:31.869 --> 00:39:35.532
We understand the problem.
Twelve Kicks from the Tam School...

327
00:39:35.706 --> 00:39:40.700
...Iron Fist from the Hung School
and the Hexagon Staff...

328
00:39:41.278 --> 00:39:43.269
Those guys at Pig Sty are really good.

329
00:39:43.447 --> 00:39:45.711
Their warrior days are long over...

330
00:39:46.217 --> 00:39:49.653
...but they're still top fighters.

331
00:39:50.054 --> 00:39:54.889
This job is a great challenge for us.

332
00:39:55.226 --> 00:39:57.751
Now. that's professionalism.

333
00:39:57.928 --> 00:40:03.264
Number One Killers. Expensive. yes.
but worth every penny!

334
00:40:03.434 --> 00:40:04.423
No!

335
00:40:04.602 --> 00:40:09.665
Number one is the Beast.
the worid's top killer.

336
00:40:10.141 --> 00:40:14.441
He was so dedicated to kung fu.
he went crazy.

337
00:40:14.612 --> 00:40:17.911
I heard he's now in an asylum.

338
00:40:18.516 --> 00:40:21.815
So you're the top killers now.

339
00:40:21.986 --> 00:40:26.355
Strictly speaking.
we're just musicians.

340
00:40:26.657 --> 00:40:31.424
<i>A song that wrenches the heart
O where do I find a knowing ear?</i>

341
00:40:31.695 --> 00:40:36.098
Great poem. isn't it?

342
00:40:44.175 --> 00:40:45.699
We'll be saying goodbye soon.

343
00:40:45.876 --> 00:40:48.367
Who knows when we'll see
each other again.

344
00:40:49.113 --> 00:40:53.311
We're three of a kind.
Wish we'd known before.

345
00:40:53.484 --> 00:40:56.783
Let's take this opportunity
to spar a little.

346
00:40:57.021 --> 00:41:00.388
No. We still have a lot to pack.

347
00:41:01.158 --> 00:41:02.887
You're right.

348
00:41:40.998 --> 00:41:44.331
Twelve Kicks of the Tam School!
Superb attack and defense!

349
00:41:44.568 --> 00:41:47.366
Iron Fist: Powerful yet delicate.
Topnotch!

350
00:41:47.538 --> 00:41:50.837
Hexagon Staff. with its
thousand moves. Mystical!

351
00:41:51.308 --> 00:41:53.640
Till we meet again!

352
00:42:03.320 --> 00:42:04.309
More lipstick!

353
00:42:23.707 --> 00:42:26.699
Stay there. or I'll break you in half.

354
00:43:50.628 --> 00:43:52.687
Sorry. we're closed.

355
00:43:52.863 --> 00:43:54.888
You can make a suit in no time.

356
00:43:55.065 --> 00:43:56.555
We're moving.

357
00:43:56.734 --> 00:43:58.565
This is good material!

358
00:43:59.236 --> 00:44:01.568
You know your stuff.

359
00:44:02.106 --> 00:44:04.267
This has high artistic value.

360
00:44:04.875 --> 00:44:06.206
How high?

361
00:44:06.644 --> 00:44:08.475
At least a few stories...

362
00:45:18.482 --> 00:45:20.712
Insulting the Axe Gang!
We'll show them.

363
00:45:20.884 --> 00:45:24.047
Let's kill them all and make
this place a brothel.

364
00:45:24.221 --> 00:45:26.212
Don't block my view!

365
00:46:15.773 --> 00:46:16.762
What's going on?

366
00:46:28.218 --> 00:46:29.344
Good!

367
00:46:29.520 --> 00:46:31.351
Don't block my view!

368
00:46:36.527 --> 00:46:39.690
Damn! I told those nitwits to leave.
but they're still here.

369
00:46:39.863 --> 00:46:41.592
- Really?
- Yeah.

370
00:47:05.155 --> 00:47:09.148
What the hell is this fighting?
Who'll pay for the damage?

371
00:47:09.326 --> 00:47:11.317
Sorry. sorry. It's nothing!
